{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-parent-of-an-element-using-jquery","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"jquery","demoType":null,"title":"Selektovanje roditeljskog elementa korišćenjem jQuery-ja","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Svaki element HTML ima element <code>parent</code> koji koristi parametre <code>inherits</code>.</p>\n<p>Na primer, element <code>h3</code> u vašem <code>jQuery Playground</code> ima roditeljski element <code>&#x3C;div class=\"container-fluid\"></code>, koji takođe ima roditeljski element <code>body</code>.</p>\n<p>jQuery ima metod nazvan <code>parent()</code> koji vam omogućava da dobijete pristup roditelju bilo kog izabranog elementa.</p>\n<p>Evo primera kako da koristite funkciju <code>parent()</code> ako želite da roditeljski element elementa <code>left-well</code> postavite plavu pozadinsku boju:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">$(\"#left-well\").parent().css(\"background-color\", \"blue\")\n</code></pre>\n<p>Daj roditelju elementa sa <code>#target1</code> pozadinom crvenoj boje.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aed308826","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18321,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-parent-of-an-element-using-jquery"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":null,"src":"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  $(document).ready(function() {\r\n    $(\"#target1\").css(\"color\", \"red\");\r\n    $(\"#target1\").prop(\"disabled\", true);\r\n    $(\"#target4\").remove();\r\n    $(\"#target2\").appendTo(\"#right-well\");\r\n    $(\"#target5\").clone().appendTo(\"#left-well\");\r\n\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Only change code above this line -->\r\n\r\n<body>\r\n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n    <h3 class=\"text-primary text-center\">jQuery Playground</h3>\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n      <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n        <h4>#left-well</h4>\r\n        <div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">\r\n          <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target1\">#target1</button>\r\n          <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target2\">#target2</button>\r\n          <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target3\">#target3</button>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n        <h4>#right-well</h4>\r\n        <div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">\r\n          <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target4\">#target4</button>\r\n          <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target5\">#target5</button>\r\n          <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target6\">#target6</button>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</body>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš element za <code>left-well</code> trebao bi imati crvenu pozadinsku boju.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  $('#left-well').css('background-color') === 'red' ||\r\n    $('#left-well').css('background-color') === 'rgb(255, 0, 0)' ||\r\n    $('#left-well').css('background-color').toLowerCase() === '#ff0000' ||\r\n    $('#left-well').css('background-color').toLowerCase() === '#f00'\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristiš funkciju <code>.parent()</code> da promeniš ovaj element.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/\\.parent\\s*\\(\\s*\\)\\s*\\.css/g));"},{"text":"<p>Putanja za <code>.parent()</code> treba da se pozove u elementu <code>#target1</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  code.match(/\\$\\s*?\\(\\s*?(?:'|\")\\s*?#target1\\s*?(?:'|\")\\s*?\\)\\s*?\\.parent/gi)\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Treba da koristiš jQuery samo da dodaš ove klase na element.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/<div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">/g));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#jquery","dashedName":"target-the-parent-of-an-element-using-jquery","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"jquery","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":null,"src":"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-children-of-an-element-using-jquery","prevChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/clone-an-element-using-jquery","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aed308826","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":6,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<script>\r\n  $(document).ready(function() {\r\n    $(\"#target1\").css(\"color\", \"red\");\r\n    $(\"#target1\").prop(\"disabled\", true);\r\n    $(\"#target4\").remove();\r\n    $(\"#target2\").appendTo(\"#right-well\");\r\n    $(\"#target5\").clone().appendTo(\"#left-well\");\r\n    $(\"#target1\").parent().css(\"background-color\", \"red\");\r\n    $(\"#right-well\").children().css(\"color\", \"orange\");\r\n    $(\"#left-well\").children().css(\"color\", \"green\");\r\n    $(\".target:nth-child(2)\").addClass(\"animated bounce\");\r\n    $(\".target:even\").addClass(\"animated shake\");\r\n    $(\"body\").addClass(\"animated hinge\");\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Only change code above this line -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"text-primary text-center\">jQuery Playground</h3>\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#left-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target1\">#target1</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target2\">#target2</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target3\">#target3</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#right-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target4\">#target4</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target5\">#target5</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target6\">#target6</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-parent-of-an-element-using-jquery"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}